✨TIP TIME✨:

3 tips for a sure fire FUN and CONFIDENT portrait session:

▪️ Music🎶 Jam out to your favorite songs before and during the session and let LOOSE. If you're having fun, it'll definitely translate over to your photos.

▪️ Clothes you feel confident in👕 If you have a pair of heels or a specific outfit that makes you feel like a million bucks, bring them, wear them! You feel better when you LOVE what you're wearing!

▪️ Keep moving💃 We've got you covered with styling and poses, just follow our direction and remember to move a smidge with each click!

We were very fortunate to shoot the Vital Voices HQ in DC earlier this year. The shoot focused on a collaboration of @farrowandball with @vitalvoices . 

"Five colors from Farrow & Ball’s signature palette are featured prominently throughout the building, each one promoting a different feeling. The standout swatches they selected and their implied meanings are: Hague Blue (Driving Force or Sense of Mission), Calke Green (Strong Roots in the Community), Incarnadine (Bold Ideas and Bold Action), Borrowed Light (Ability to Connect Across Lines That Divide), and Brinjal (Paying It Forward)." 

Vital Voices is a "nonprofit organization that seeks to invest in and amplify the voices of female leaders and change-makers across the world". 

Writer @lydiageisel for @dominomag
